#include<iostream>
#include<algorithm>
#include<cmath>

using namespace std;

int checksum(int x)
{
    int sum = 0;
    while(x>0)
    {
        sum = sum + x%10;
        x/=10;
    }
    
    if(sum==2||sum==3||sum==5||sum==7||sum==11||sum==13||sum==17||sum==19||sum==23||sum==29||sum==31||sum==37)
    return 1;
    else return 0;
    
    
}




int main()
{int t,l,u,count,i;
cin>>t;
while(t--)
{   count=0;
    cin>>l>>u;
    for(i=l;i<=u;i++)
    { if(checksum(i))
       count++;
        
    }
    
    
    cout<<count<<endl;
    
}
    return 0;
}
